1
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:10,480
I've known that Immortal Xiyin

2
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,400
once showed you great kindness.

3
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:14,080
How did you know?

4
00:00:14,920 --> 00:00:16,280
What are you really after?

5
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:17,560
Relax.

6
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:19,600
We're on the same side.

7
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:21,880
Although she's been reborn,

8
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:24,160
Xieyun is controlling her
from within her body.

9
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:26,000
She has no memories of her past life.

10
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:27,600
Don't you...

11
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,000
want to help her?

12
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:31,760
Xieyun?

13
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:34,280
Let I ask you,

14
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:36,160
do you want to help her or not?

15
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:38,800
How?

16
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:41,760
It's both simple

17
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,920
and difficult.

18
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:44,520
You have to...

19
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:48,080
make her fall in love with you.

20
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:54,320
Fall in love with me?

21
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:58,600
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 6]

22
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:23,520
Master.

23
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:25,640
Will you blame me

24
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:29,520
for doing this?

25
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,840
Even if you do,

26
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,360
it's fine.

27
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,520
All I want is for you
to come back to life.

28
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,080
As long as you can live again,

29
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:41,280
even if I'm torn to pieces
or doomed forever,

30
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,480
I won't hesitate.

31
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,040
She's about this tall.

32
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:48,920
She came from over there.

33
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:49,560
Have you seen her?

34
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,320
No.

35
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:52,320
Miss,

36
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,440
have you seen a young lady?

37
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:54,600
About this tall.

38
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,280
Have you?

39
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:55,920
No.

40
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,160
Where could she have gone?

41
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,960
Did she go back to Fuxian Abode?

42
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,000
Ruoxi.

43
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,080
Ruoxi!

44
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,320
Ruoxi.

45
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:20,880
What's wrong?

46
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,120
What happened?

47
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,480
Has Ruoxi come back?

48
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:24,560
Didn't she

49
00:02:24,900 --> 00:02:26,400
go out with you?

50
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,880
She's missing.

51
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,960
Ruoxi is missing.

52
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,120
Maybe she's just being playful

53
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,400
and ran off somewhere?

54
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:35,720
That's impossible.

55
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,280
I've searched the whole town.

56
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:38,680
I found

57
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,880
the half-eaten tanghulu she left behind.

58
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:40,620
She'd never just

59
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:41,900
leave her tanghulu on the ground.

60
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:43,720
What's wrong?

61
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:45,680
Ruoxi...

62
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:47,400
She's missing.

63
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,120
What did you say?

64
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,720
The hairstyle and clothes are different.

65
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:15,480
You're up.

66
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:16,960
Let me show you

67
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,040
my swordplay.

68
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,600
Have you seen this young lady?

69
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,040
- No.
- No.

70
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,640
Have you seen this young lady?

71
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:49,320
No.

72
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,680
Have you seen this young lady?

73
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,520
No.

74
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,600
Have you seen this young lady?

75
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,760
No.

76
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,600
Ruoxi.

77
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,880
Where did you go?

78
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:43,960
You...

79
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:46,880
You're awake.

80
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:47,960
You...

81
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,680
You're a bad guy.

82
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:52,320
You must be hungry.

83
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,400
Have something to eat.

84
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,040
I won't.

85
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,080
Let me go right now!

86
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,200
Do you remember this place?

87
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,800
Heng, you're the best.

88
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,760
You know osmanthus cake is my favorite.

89
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,280
Is it good?

90
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:42,720
This

91
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,720
is your favorite osmanthus cake.

92
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,680
I don't like osmanthus cakes!

93
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,800
Let me go!

94
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:52,960
I almost forgot.

95
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,200
You're not my junior sister.

96
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,960
You just look exactly like her.

97
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:01,200
Junior sister?

98
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,320
What is

99
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,200
a "master"?

100
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:06,520
A master

101
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,920
is someone who teaches skills.

102
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,920
Is the "junior sister" you mentioned

103
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,280
a master?

104
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,960
The one

105
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,880
who teaches skills?

106
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,840
You just said

107
00:06:22,260 --> 00:06:23,720
I look like

108
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,720
your junior sister?

109
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,200
With me here,

110
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,640
I'll keep you safe.

111
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:42,960
Heng?

112
00:06:47,260 --> 00:06:47,760
Xiyin.

113
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:52,560
Xiyin.

114
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,400
Eat first, then you'll have the strength
to find her.

115
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,680
I'm not hungry. You guys go ahead.

116
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,440
I'm not hungry either.

117
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:21,360
You guys...

118
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,000
Then I won't eat either.

119
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,160
The hardest part

120
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,880
of the Shadow Resurrection Art
isn't collecting

121
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,280
your master's soul fragments,

122
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:59,880
or putting them back together.

123
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,520
The real challenge

124
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:04,840
is getting Bai Ruoxi, a blank slate,

125
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,120
to develop emotions and desires

126
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:08,480
in just three months.

127
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,720
So that's why you said from the start

128
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,720
I might not succeed.

129
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,760
This forbidden art

130
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,920
has precedents in the Shadow Clan.

131
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,880
It's just that
no one has ever succeeded.

132
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,320
Master.

133
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,480
Where have you gone?

134
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:40,920
Xiyin.

135
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,760
You sacrificed yourself
for the sake of all living beings.

136
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,200
The world

137
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:48,200
praises your selflessness.

138
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:49,640
Now,

139
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,200
I absolutely can't let this fiend

140
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:55,040
ruin your reputation.

141
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,660
Where am I?

142
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:11,520
What do you want to do to me?

143
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,320
I've been here before?

144
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:22,720
Yes.

145
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:24,400
This

146
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,920
is where you were created.

147
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,360
Can you please let me go back?

148
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:30,520
I want to go home.

149
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,800
Yaoyang would be upset

150
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,000
if he couldn't find me.

151
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,800
I don't want him to be sad.

152
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,240
I'm begging you, let me go back.

153
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:40,680
Xiyin.

154
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,560
Forgive me.

155
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,800
I have to go home.

156
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,440
No one will stop me!

157
00:10:39,660 --> 00:10:42,400
♪What is flickering?♪

158
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:45,140
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

159
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:51,140
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

160
