♪What is falling?♪

161
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:57,260
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

162
00:10:57,500 --> 00:11:02,700
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

163
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:05,220
♪When petals drift down♪

164
00:11:05,260 --> 00:11:06,720
♪When the rain falls all around♪

165
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:09,420
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

166
00:11:09,580 --> 00:11:11,280
♪Beyond the dunes♪

167
00:11:11,380 --> 00:11:12,660
♪No end in sight♪

168
